%20the%20man%20from%20the%20craft%2C%20and%20reduce%20logistics%20footprint%20over%20the%20Improved%20Ribbon%20Bridge%20in%20use%20today%20by%20combining%20both%20payload%20capacity%20and%20powertrain%20into%20a%20single%20craft%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Army's%20Small%20Business%20Innovation%20Research%20(SBIR)%20solicitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20not%20coincidentally%2C%20the%20proposal%20comes%20as%20even%20the%20Army's%20own%20engineers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-us-army-isnt-ready-to-attack-across-rivers-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equestion%3C%2Fa%3E%20whether%20it%20has%20adequate%20bridge-building%20capabilities%2C%20especially%20for%20%26quot%3Bwet%20gap%26quot%3B%20assaults%20across%20defended%20river%20lines.%20While%20the%20Army%20became%20proficient%20in%20such%20operations%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20such%20as%20attacking%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwarfarehistorynetwork.com%2Farticle%2Foperation-plunder-crossing-the-rhine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERhine%20River%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201945%2C%20decades%20of%20counterinsurgency%20warfare%20has%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20skills%20such%20as%20erecting%20bridges%20capable%20of%20bearing%20heavy%20vehicles%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-operation-builds-cage-armor-protect-us-made-abrams-tanks-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EM1%20Abrams%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20also%20worry%20that%20there%20aren't%20enough%20bridge-building%20units.%20Or%2C%20that%20Army%20divisions%20lack%20sufficient%20river-crossing%20resources%20without%20additional%20engineering%20support%20from%20corps%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20wake-up%20call%20has%20been%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-wrecked-russian-tanks-destroyed-in-failed-river-crossing-2022-5%5C%22%20ta