in%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20it's%20an%20interesting%20case%2C%20I%20get%20to%20deal%20with%20other%20smart%20people.%20We%20get%20to%20talk%20about%20it.%20We%20get%20to%20look%20things%20up%20constantly%20and%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20looking%20for%20weeks%20of%20quiet%20time.%20I'm%20not%20even%20sure%20I'd%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-older-americans-still-working-retirement-social-security-unretiring-doctor-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739696641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae642ceb4be2fff9a49e6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-older-americans-still-working-retirement-social-security-unretiring-doctor-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20older%20Americans%20are%20still%20working%20into%20their%20retirement%20years%2C%20even%20though%20they're%20millionaires%20and%20could%20easily%20retire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40businessinsider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A112%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-older-americans-still-working-retirement-social-security-unretiring-doctor-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20has%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20build%20resilient%20housing%20in%20disaster-prone%20places%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20here's%20what%20the%20US%20can%20learn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tokyo%20Skyline%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ace55ceb4be2fff9a46c37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221921%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJapan%20has%20taken%20steps%20in%20recent%20decades%20to%20make%20its%20homes%20and%20build