ly%20Stampede%3A%20Railways%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20devotees%20from%20across%20India%20have%20been%20visiting%20the%20ongoing%20Maha%20Kumbh%20mela%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%20-%20one%20that%20is%20held%20every%2012%20years%20-%20causing%20a%20huge%20rush%20in%20trains%20and%20traffic%20on%20roads.%20A%20wave%20of%20stampede-like%20incidents%20and%20angry%20passengers%20breaking%20train%20windows%20as%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20board%20the%20train%20to%20Maha%20Kumbh%20amid%20the%20rush%20have%20come%20to%20light%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20night%2C%20at%20least%2018%20people%2C%20including%2011%20women%20and%20five%20children%2C%20died%20after%20a%20huge%20crowd%20of%20passengers%20caused%20by%20two%20delayed%20trains%20and%20a%20special%20Express%20train%20to%20Maha%20Kumbh%20led%20to%20a%20stampede%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-maha-kumbh-rush-train-delays-led-to-new-delhi-railway-station-stampede-prayagraj-express-7721219%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20Railway%20statio%3C%2Fa%3En.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20eyewitnesses%20claimed%20that%20the%20stampede%20took%20place%20after%20a%20rumour%20spread%20among%20people%20that%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%20was%20going%20to%20arrive%20on%20a%20different%20platform%2C%20the%20Railway%20authorities%20have%20repeatedly%20denied%20it.%20Himanshu%20Shekhar%20Upadhyay%2C%20CPRO%20Northern%20Railway%20said%20that%20there%20was%20already%20a%20huge%20rush%20on%20the%20station's%20platform%20when%20a%20passenger%20slipped%20on%20the%20nearby%20stairs%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-delhi-railway-station-chaos-deaths-live-updates-maha-kumbh-mela-prayagraj-7719911%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeadly%20stamped%3C%2Fa%3Ee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20official%2C%20platforms%20number%2013%20and%2014%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20station%20were%20already%20crowded%20as%20many%20people%20were%20waiting%20to%20board%20two%20trains%20-%20Magdh%20Express%20and%20another%20going%20towards%20Jammu%20-%20which%20were%20delayed.%20Amid%20this%2C%20a%20special%20train%20for%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%2C%20was%20to%20leave%20at%2010%3A10%20pm%20from%20platform%20number%2014.%20As%20the%20time%20for%20the%20train%20to%20Prayagraj%20neared%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20started%20gathering%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20existing%20rush.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20general%20tickets%20were%20bought%20by%20passengers%20to%20go%20to%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrains%20were%20not%20cancelled%2C%20and%20the%20platform%20was%20not%20changed.%20All%20trains%20have%20been%20running%20as%20per%20its%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%20has%20also%20formed%20a%20two-member%20high-level%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20incident.%C2%A0Narsingh%20Deo%2C%20Principal%20Chief%20Commercial%20Manager%20of%20Northern%20Railway%20and%20Pankaj%20Gangwar%2C%20Principal%20Chief%20Security%20Commissioner%20of%20Northern%20Railway%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%2C%20which%20has%20commenced%20its%20inquiry%2C%20gave%20orders%20to%20secure%20all%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Railways%20is%20managing%20Maha%20Kumbh%20rush%20in%20Prayagraj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20millions%20of%20people%20are%20visiting%20Prayagraj%2C%20the%20railway%20authorities%20have%20made%20extensive%20security%20measures%20across%20the%20city's%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashikant%20Tripathi%2C%20CRPO%20of%20North%20Central%20Railway%20told%20NDTV%20that%20they%20have%20been%20maintaining%20protocol%20at%20all%20railway%20stations%20in%20the%20city.%20%26quot%3BThrough%20these%20protocols%2C%20either%20on%20normal%20day%20rush%20or%20key%20days%20like%20'mauni%20amavasiya'%2C%20we%20have%20made%20a%20smooth%20entry%20and%20exit%20for%20passengers.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20colour-coded%20areas%2C%20we%20have%20helped%20the%20passengers%20board%20and%20deboard%20trains%20safely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20they%20do%20not%20need%20to%20enforce%20any%20new%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20working%20well%20with%20these%20protocols.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Prayagraj%20junction%2C%20we%20only%20allow%20the%20passengers%20to%20enter%20through%20the%20city%20side%20and%20the%20exit%20is%20done%20through%20civil%20lines%20side.%20We%20have%204%20passenger%20sheds%20which%20are%20colour-coded%20and%20directions%20have%20been%20defined%20on%20them.%20Whenever%20the%20limit%20of%20passengers%20crosses%20at%20these%20sheds%2C%20we%20activate%20the%20Kusrow%20Bagh%20area%20-%20from%20where%20the%20passengers%20can%20travel.%20All%20basic%20amenities%20have%20also%20been%20provided%20at%20these%20locations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739692800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F74nt1b3_stampede_625x300_16_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-railways-said-on-stampede-at-new-delhi-railway-station-that-killed-18-passengers-maha-kumbh-2025-maha-kumbh-prayagraj-7722345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2018%20people%20died%20after%20a%20huge%20crowd%20of%20passengers%20caused%20by%20two%20delayed%20trains%20and%20a%20special%20Express%20train%20to%20Maha%20Kumbh%20led%20to%20a%20stampede%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20station.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBe%20Kind%20To%20Yourself%26quot%3B%3A%20Vikrant%20Massey%2C%20Bhumi%20Pednekar%20On%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStudy%20to%20pass%20in%20life%2C%20not%20just%20exams%2C%20and%20identify%20your%20strengths%20during%20challenging%20times%2C%20actors%20Vikrant%20Massey%20and%20Bhumi%20Pednekar%20told%20school%20students%20during%20an%20interaction%20on%20PM's%20Parisha%20Pe%20Charcha%20aired%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20actors%20shared%20their%20school%20experiences%2C%20tackling%20exam%20stress%2C%20parental%20expectations%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20resilience%20at%20a%20special%20session%20of%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%20(PPC)%2C%20an%20annual%20event%20in%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20interacts%20with%20students%20appearing%20for%20board%20examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shift%20from%20the%20traditional%20town%20hall%20format%2C%20this%20time%20the%20prime%20minister%20preferred%20a%20more%20informal%20setting%20and%20took%20the%20students%20to%20Delhi's%20iconic%20Sunder%20Nursery%20for%20his%20annual%20interaction%20with%20them%20ahead%20of%20board%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMassey%2C%20who%20saw%20a%20career%20turnaround%20with%20the%202023%20film%20%26quot%3B12th%20Fail%26quot%3B%2C%20asked%20students%20to%20practice%20the%20%26quot%3Bpower%20of%20visualisation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20how%20to%20subconsciously%20visualise.%20You%20can%20take%20out%2010%20minutes%20a%20day%20to%20write%20about%20your%20feelings%20and%20what%20you%20wish%20to%20achieve%20in%20a%20journal...%20It's%20a%20kind%20of%20manifestation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNever%20feel%20arrogant%20about%20getting%20good%20marks.%20Keep%20your%20eyes%20low%20and%20your%20thinking%20high.%20That's%20very%20important.%20Study%20to%20pass%20in%20life%2C%20not%20just%20exams.%20Be%20kind%20to%20yourself%20and%20if%20you%20do%20not%20meet%20your%20expectations%2C%20restart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20time%20she%20lost%20her%20father%2C%20Pednekar%20said%20she%20was%20very%20young%20when%20she%20realised%20she%20had%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20age%20you%20don't%20realise%20that%20such%20a%20big%20unfortunate%20event%20has%20happened%20to%20you.%20I%20just%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20play%20by%20my%20strengths.%20Identify%20your%20strengths%20during%20challenging%20times...%20Explore%20new%20ways%20to%20learn...%20Like%20whenever%20I%20am%20given%20a%20scene%2C%20I%20try%20doing%20it%20in%20different%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BDum%20Laga%20Ke%20Haisha%26quot%3B%20actor%20said%20during%20the%20eighth%20edition%20of%20PPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20school%20days%2C%20Massey%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20above%20average%20student%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20more%20into%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20pick%20up%20books%20days%20before%20exams.%20We%20had%20cable%20TV%20at%20the%20time%20so%20that%20used%20to%20be%20disconnected%20during%20exams...%20I'm%20a%20bit%20sad%20to%20see%20today's%20generation.%20Our%20playtime%20was%20all%20about%20the%20playground.%20For%20today's%20generation%2C%20it's%20mobile.%20Cricket%2C%20which%20is%20our%20country's%20most%20favourite%20sport%2C%20requires%20one%20to%20be%20present%20in%20the%20moment.%20Even%20the%20prime%20minister%20says%20'The%20present%20is%20God's%20favourite%20present'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPednekar%20too%20said%20she%20was%20never%20a%20frontbencher%20and%20used%20to%20enjoy%20participating%20in%20extracurricular%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20very%20obedient%20student%20and%20I%20still%20am.%20I%20was%20mischievous%20but%20I%20shared%20a%20beautiful%20relationship%20with%20my%20teachers...%20I%20realised%20early%20on%20that%20I%20want%20to%20be%20an%20actor.%20I%20wanted%20my%20parents%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20proud%20so%20I%20used%20to%20work%20very%20hard%20in%20studies.%26quot%3B%20Children%20are%20unable%20to%20grow%20when%20the%20expectations%20of%20parents%20start%20to%20feel%20like%20a%20burden%2C%20added%20Massey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExpress%20yourself.%20If%20your%20parents%20want%20you%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20but%20you%20want%20to%20become%20a%20photographer%2C%20you%20should%20tell%20them%20what%20you%20feel.%20They%20will%20get%20convinced%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%20because%20all%20they%20want%20for%20you%20is%20to%20be%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPednekar%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20good%20sleep%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20take%20an%20hour-long%20break%20in%20a%20day%20during%20exams.%20I%20would%20go%20out%20and%20play%2C%20I%20loved%20dancing%2C%20playing%20badminton.%20All%20that%20was%20important%20for%20me%20was%20to%20give%20my%20brain%20a%20break...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20young%2C%20I%20just%20didn't%20want%20to%20sleep.%20Now%20when%20I'm%20shooting%2C%20I%20quickly%20finish%20my%20lunch%20in%2015%20minutes%20and%20sleep%20for%20half%20an%20hour.%20That%20half%20an%20hour%20of%20sleep%20will%20give%20me%20a%20very%20focused%20eight%20hours%20at%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMassey%20shared%20his%20three%20hacks%20on%20how%20to%20be%20an%20'Exam%20Warrior'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEat%20well%2C%20rest%20well%3B%20keep%20improving%3B%20and%20go%2C%20play%2C%20unplug%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20to%20give%20her%20go-to%20tips%20to%20handle%20stress%2C%20Pednekar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BBe%20a%20warrior%2C%20not%20a%20worrier.%20Being%20spiritual%20keeps%20you%20grounded%20and%20focused.%26quot%3B%20Previously%2C%20eminent%20personalities%20like%20boxer%20MC%20Mary%20Kom%2C%20spiritual%20leader%20Sadhguru%2C%20and%20Bollywood%20star%20Deepika%20Padukone%20also%20shared%20their%20experiences%20and%20knowledge%20with%20students%20on%20k