ndia's%20middle-order.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20report%20has%20claimed%20that%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20aren't%20on%20the%20same%20page%20over%20the%20selection%20cases%20of%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20prompting%20a%20heated%20debate%20in%20the%20team%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India's%20preliminary%20Champions%20Trophy%20squad%20was%20picked%2C%20Agarkar%20had%20labelled%20Rishabh%20Pant%20as%20the%20No.%201%20wicket-keeper%20in%20the%20team.%20But%2C%20he%20didn't%20play%20a%20single%20ODI%20against%20England.%20After%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20series%2C%20head%20coach%20Gambhir%20clarified%20that%20KL%20Rahul%20is%20India's%20No.%201%20wicket-keeper%20in%20ODIs.%20The%20contradictory%20statements%20from%20the%20two%20pillars%20of%20the%20management%20don't%20paint%20a%20pleasant%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20it's%20very%20difficult%20to%20talk%20about%20individuals%2C%20but%20all%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20if%20Pant%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20squad%2C%20he%20will%20get%20an%20opportunity.%20But%20at%20the%20moment%20obviously%2C%20KL%20is%20our%20number%20one%20wicketkeeper%2C%20and%20he's%20delivered%20for%20us.%20When%20you%20have%20two%20wicketkeepers%20in%20the%20squad%2C%20you%20can't%20play%20both%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20quality%20we've%20got.%20Hopefully%2C%20whenever%20he%20%5BPant%5D%20gets%20an%20opportunity%2C%20he%20should%20be%20ready%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gambhir%20had%20said%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20ODI%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20ODI%20against%20England%2C%20the%20team%20had%20initially%20intended%20to%20keep%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20while%20giving%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20chance%20at%20the%20top.%20But%2C%20an%20injury%20to%20Virat%20Kohli%20meant%20that%20Iyer%20played%20at%20the%20usual%20No.%203%20spot%2C%20cracking%20a%20fiery%20half-century.%20The%20batter%2C%20since%20then%2C%20became%20a%20regular%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20matches%20of%20the%20series.%20But%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20some%20conflict%20in%20the%20team%20management%20over%20Iyer's%20case%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Findias-middle-order-a-concern-ahead-of-champions-trophy%2Farticleshow%2F118292491.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20selector%20Devang%20Gandhi%20lauded%20India%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20helping%20the%20Indian%20team%20manage%20this%20transition%20but%20he%20also%20warned%20him%20to%20bring%20more%20consistency%20in%20the%20middle-order%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGambhir%20must%20be%20given%20due%20credit%20for%20working%20with%20a%20team%20in%20transition.%20He%20has%20got%20India%20dominating%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%2C%20much%20like%20India%20were%20doing%20from%202016-2019.%20What%20the%20selectors%20and%20Gambhir%20need%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20is%20consistency%20in%20the%20middle%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20Gandhi%20told%20TOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20batting%20then%20was%20largely%20driven%20by%20the%20top%20three%20-%20Rohit%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shikhar%20Dhawan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F737-shikhar-dhawan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShikhar%20Dhawan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Virat%20Kohli.%20What%20happened%20then%20was%20nobody%20else%20got%20time%20to%20settle%20down%20from%20No.%204%20onwards.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20batting%20wasn't%20sure%20of%20the%20role%20they%20had%20to%20play.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20top%20order%20collapsed%20in%20those%20big%20matches%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20batting%20looked%20clueless.%20Hopefully%2C%20it%20isn't%20the%20case%20this%20time.%20If%20they%20have%20identified%20Axar%20as%20a%20No.%205%20batter%20then%20they%20must%20look%20to%20give%20him%20a%20run%20at%20that%20number.%20Axar%20has%20done%20well%20but%20the%20management%20has%20to%20decide%20if%20he%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20long-term%20option%20who%20can%20rebuild%20and%20dominate%20an%20innings%20till%20the%202027%20World%20Cup%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%26quot%3B%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20of%20the%20three%20ODIs%20against%20England%2C%20the%20management%20promoted%20bowling%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20move%20that%20baffled%20many.%20Gandhi%20feels%20even%20the%20decision%20to%20bench%20Iyer%2C%20though%20it%20couldn't%20be%20fulfilled%2C%20didn't%20make%20any%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20to%20bench%20Iyer%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20series%20didn't%20make%20any%20sense%2C%20since%20Iyer%20has%20been%20exceptional%20in%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20and%20India%20have%20played%20very%20few%20ODIs%20afte