%20pm%2C%20crowds%20on%20the%20overbridge%20between%20platforms%2014%20and%2015%20were%20so%20large%20that%20even%20the%20police%20were%20rendered%20helpless.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20platform%20change.%20This%20incident%20happened%20despite%20special%20trains%20running%20every%2030%20minutes%20all%20through%20the%20night.%20In%20my%2026%20years%20at%20this%20station%2C%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20crowd%2C%20not%20even%20on%20Chhath%20Puja.%20So%20much%20force%20was%20deployed%2C%20including%20the%20NDRF%2C%20but%20people%20were%20not%20paying%20heed%20to%20their%20instructions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Stampede%20at%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%20%7C%20An%20eyewitness%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20crowd%20was%20beyond%20the%20limit%2C%20people%20were%20gathered%20at%20the%20(foot%20over)%20bridge...%20Such%20a%20huge%20crowd%20wasn't%20expected.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20massive%20crowd%20at%20the%20railway%20station%2C%20even%20during%20the%20festivals.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHt6xJjNPpc%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHt6xJjNPpc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1890923829213733375%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20and%2011%20other%20members%20of%20his%20family%20were%20to%20board%20the%2010.10%20pm%20train%20to%20Prayagraj%2C%20but%20they%20never%20made%20it%20round%20the%20platform.%20A%20crowd%20descended%20even%20before%20they%20could%20climb%20down%20stairs%20and%20swept%20over%20them%20and%20many%20others.%20While%20they%20pulled%20out%20his%20daughter%20and%20sister-in-law%20from%20the%20chaotic%20situation%20alive%2C%20his%20sister%20was%20found%2030%20minutes%20later%2C%20showing%20no%20signs%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20conducted%20CPR%20on%20her%20for%20one%20hours.%20All%20this%20while%2C%20no%20authorities%20came%20for%20help.%20I%20had%20to%20carry%20her%20body%20across%20the%20railway%20tracks%20to%20rush%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Stampede%20at%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%20%7C%20At%20LNJP%20hospital%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20one%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%2012%20people%20going%20to%20Maha%20Kumbh.%20We%20hadn't%20even%20reached%20the%20platform%20but%20were%20at%20the%20stairs...%20My%20family%2C%20including%20my%20sister%20were%20stuck%20in%20the%20crowd.%20We%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYzcnurcmdO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYzcnurcmdO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1890920503973700059%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20had%20an%20inkling%20that%20something%20was%20amiss%20since%205%20pm%20on%20Saturday%20when%20it%20took%20him%20one%20hour%20to%20exit%20New%20Delhi%20Metro%20station%2C%20which%20usually%20takes%20just%20two%20minutes.%20He%20was%20also%20present%20when%20the%20stampede%20on%20Mauni%20Amawasya%20occurred%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20killing%2030%20people%2C%20and%20saw%20a%20pattern%20in%20the%20way%20the%20crowds%20swelled%20in%20no%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20climbed%20down%20to%20Platforms%2013%20and%2014%20and%20shouted%20and%20urged%20passengers%20to%20wait%20for%202-3%20days%20and%20then%20travel%20to%20Prayagraj%20if%20they%20can't%20find%20a%20place%20today.%20What%20can%20the%20authorities%20do%20to%20manage%20a%20crowd%20of%2010%2C000%20people%20that%20is%20not%20listening%20to%20their%20instructions.%20People%20continued%20to%20rush%20to%20whichever%20platform%20there%20was%20an%20announcement%20for%20regarding%20a%20train%20leaving%20for%20Prayagraj.%20I%20helped%20pick%20up%203-4%20people%20and%20put%20them%20in%20Delhi%20Police%20cars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20passenger%20Pramod%20Chaurasia%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20sleeper-class%20ticket%20for%20Purushottam%20Express%20but%20even%20those%20with%20confirmed%20tickets%20could%20not%20board%20the%20train.%20One%20of%20my%20friends%20and%20a%20female%20passenger%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20crowd.%20There%20was%20too%20much%20pushing%20and%20jostling.%20We%20managed%20to%20stay%20safe%20by%20waiting%20outside%20with%20our%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police%20(railway)%20said%20platform%20number%2014%20was%20already%20very%20crowded%20when%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%20train%20was%20waiting%20there%20for%20its%20departure.%20The%20officer%20said%20Swatantra%20Senani%20Express%20and%20Bhubaneshwar%20Rajdhani%20Express%20were%20delayed%20and%20the%20passengers%20of%20these%20trains%20were%20also%20present%20on%20platform%20numbers%2012%2C%2013%20and%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20CMI%2C%20every%20hour%201%2C500%20general%20tickets%20were%20sold%20by%20railways%20due%20to%20which%20the%20station%20got%20overcrowded%20and%20became%20uncontrollable.%20There%20was%20a%20stampede%20at%20platform%20no.%2014%20and%20near%20escalator%20near%20platform%20no.%2016%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DCP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20stampede%20broke%20out%20around%209.55%20pm%2C%20eyewitnesses%20said