.com%2Findia-news%2F4-pass-out-due-to-suffocation-after-huge-kumbh-rush-at-delhi-railway-station-7719417%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estampede%20at%20the%20NDLS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20broke%20out%20around%2010%20pm%2C%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20swell%20in%20the%20crowd%20of%20passengers%20waiting%20to%20board%20trains%20for%20Prayagraj%20on%20platform%20numbers%2014%20and%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20were%20pushing%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20man%20whose%20mother%20died%20in%20the%20stampede%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20passenger%20said%20the%20station%20was%20%26quot%3Bovercrowded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20going%20to%20Prayagraj%20but%20many%20trains%20were%20running%20late%20or%20were%20cancelled.%20The%20station%20was%20overcrowded.%20There%20were%20far%20more%20people%20than%20I%20have%20ever%20seen%20at%20this%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station%20Stampede%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20said%20platform%20number%2014%20was%20very%20crowded%20when%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%20train%20was%20waiting%20there%20for%20its%20departure.%20He%20said%20two%20other%20trains%20-%20%C2%A0Swatantra%20Senani%20Express%20and%20Bhubaneshwar%20Rajdhani%20Express%20-%20%C2%A0were%20delayed%20and%20the%20passengers%20of%20these%20trains%20were%20also%20present%20on%20platform%20numbers%2012%2C%2013%20and%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20CMI%20(Commercial-cum-Ticket%20Inspector)%2C%20every%20hour%201%2C500%20general%20tickets%20were%20sold%20by%20railways%20due%20to%20which%20the%20station%20got%20overcrowded%20and%20became%20uncontrollable.%20There%20was%20a%20stampede%20at%20platform%20no%2014%20and%20near%20escalator%20near%20platform%20no%2016%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20have%20grieved%20the%20d