20get%20too%20caught%20up%20in%20how%20cohesive%20their%20children's%20names%20are.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221761d9ec-13be-48d2-89b8-55c319d39ca4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDecide%20what%20unites%20your%20sibling%20set%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20easiest%20way%20to%20create%20a%20sibling%20set%20of%20names%20is%20to%20think%20about%20a%20style%20category%20of%20names%20that%20you%20like.%20If%20you're%20into%20classic%20names%20like%20John%2C%20they'll%20always%20go%20well%20with%20other%20classics%2C%20like%20Dorothy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOr%2C%20you%20can%20focus%20on%20name%20meanings.%20Nature-inspired%20names%20like%20Sky%20and%20Juniper%20can%20make%20good%20sibling%20sets%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20option%20is%20to%20think%20about%20length.%20I%20find%20that%20four-letter%20names%20often%20go%20well%20together.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it's%20OK%20to%20put%20together%20short%20and%20long%20names%20if%20they%20have%20a%20similar%20style.%20I%20love%20the%20sibling%20set%20Ada%20and%20Bernadette%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2c2a7e0-8d0b-4a83-ba45-8618e6bf218e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESubtlety%20goes%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20worked%20with%20baby%20company%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jojomamanbebe.co.uk%2Fshop%2Ff%2Fpersonalised-canbepersonalised%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20JoJo%20Maman%20B%C3%A9b%C3%A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20do's%20and%20don'ts%20of%20sibling%20sets%2C%20I%20reminded%20parents%20that%20subtlety%20goes%20a%20long%20way.%20If%20your%20theme%20is%20too%20niche%2C%20it%20can%20come%20across%20as%20cheesy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20would%20never%20name%20sisters%20Goldie%2C%20Violet%2C%20and%20Scarlett%2C%20or%20brothers%20Bear%20and%20Fox%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20little%20too%20on%20the%20n